CCTV footage of a couple being robbed outside the Helderwyk Estate, opposite Carnival City has surfaced. In the video, a Ford Ranger can be seen pulling up at the entrance of the estate, when suddenly two men run towards the driver’s side. They then pull the driver out of the bakkie, seconds later one of the robbers can be seen coming back to the driver’s side taking something and then he runs away. According to News24 the couple was robbed of two Rolex watches, a 5-carat diamond wedding ring and a diamond tennis bracelet.  SOURCE: NEWS24 